"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-christophe-dubi-ioc-paris-2024-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"International Olympic Committee Executive Director Christophe Dubi spoke with OlympicTalk aboutthe Paris 2024 economic impact report published May 14, which estimated the Games will generate at least $7.2 billion in net economic benefits in the Paris region, plus other matters regarding future Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 99, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5100005083662763e-36, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"OlympicTalk\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 89}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 176}, {\"ngram\": \"net economic benefits\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"other matters\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"future Olympic Games\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This interview has been lightly edited for clarity.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This interview\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OlympicTalk:In your opinion, what were the one or two highlights from the economic impact report?\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your opinion\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"the one or two highlights\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"the economic impact report\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dubi:The highlight is that the Olympics is a great business.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The highlight\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"a great business\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You host the Games for many reasons.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"many reasons\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But you also host the Games because it's great business, and by signing the host contract seven years before the Games, you generate an extra 7 to 11 billion euro of additional economic activity.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"great business\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the host contract\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra 7 to 11 billion euro\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"additional economic activity\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means a lot, because it means that you have been able to catalyze a number of projects.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"projects\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have been able to think about the social development in the tougher areas.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the social development\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the tougher areas\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have been able to envision the legacy and how the Games can transform.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then you look at it from an economic standpoint, and you say, on top of everything else, it's a great business.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an economic standpoint\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"a great business\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, for me, was the best possible read.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best possible read\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also put in parallel another number that came out about the same time as the economic report: the fiscal revenues generated from this extra economic impact, and they estimate between 5 to 5.3 billion euro.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parallel\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"another number\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the economic report\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the fiscal revenues\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"this extra economic impact\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"between 5 to 5.3 billion euro\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is how it all comes together, because if you take the investment of the French authorities, plus the cost of a number of services, such as security, transport and others, once you have generated the 5.3 billion euro, you look at your investment and the services, you are still black in accounting terms, and I really liked that.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8242334232329837, \"rank\": 0.21317628525948745, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the investment\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"services\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"transport\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5.3 billion euro\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"your investment\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"the services\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"accounting terms\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OlympicTalk: You have mentioned this being the first Olympics aligned withOlympic Agenda 2020 reformsin organizing and putting on the Games.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first Olympics\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"withOlympic Agenda 2020 reformsin organizing\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you tell me specifically how Agenda 2020 is implemented into the findings of this economic report?\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Agenda\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"the findings\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"this economic report\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dubi:In Agenda 2020, you had a number of strands of activities.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Agenda\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"strands\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"activities\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One was to simplify the host candidature and make it a partnership process between the IOC and the future organizing committees.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.797528746181039e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the host candidature\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"the future organizing committees\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We said the Games have to adapt to the city and region.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"region\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant that Paris was able to make the best choice according to their conditions.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2212, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best choice\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"their conditions\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant, yes, hosting shooting in Chateauroux and preliminaries of basketball and finals of handball in Lille, and that's OK. You have much more flexibility in the implementation of the host contract because we (the IOC) impose far less.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"score\": 0.9953107193992694, \"rank\": 0.004711373552492018, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\"}, {\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.797528746181039e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chateauroux\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"preliminaries\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"handball\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"much more flexibility\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the implementation\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"the host contract\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You design the solutions the way you want to.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the solutions\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that you have far more flexibility, and for that matter of Paris, designing something that makes sense from a long-term perspective, but also makes sense from an economic standpoint.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2635, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"far more flexibility\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"that matter\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-term perspective\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"an economic standpoint\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not building but using existing or temporary solutions means less investment.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"existing or temporary solutions\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"less investment\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By using public transportation rather than a full dedicated fleet of buses and cars, it means reductions of costs of one of the key items.\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"a full dedicated fleet\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2903}, {\"ngram\": \"buses\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"reductions\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the key items\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using the grid rather than generators for many of the venues means cost of energy goes down and means that the ecological impact is reduced.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the grid\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"generators\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"cost\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecological impact\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So all of these things that were made possible by the vision at the time, in the implementation vision through Agenda 2020, in the implementation by the organizing committee and the smart solutions they could find, you generate exactly this.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these things\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"the vision\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"the implementation vision\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"Agenda\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"the implementation\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizing committee\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"the smart solutions\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly this\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less impact from the environment standpoint.\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Less impact\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3371}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment standpoint\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A socially fabulous impact - creation of jobs, creation of venues, an athletes' village where it matters and30 minutes of physical activity in schools per day.\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A socially fabulous impact - creation\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"creation\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"an athletes' village\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3492}, {\"ngram\": \"and30 minutes\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"physical activity\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3544}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OlympicTalk: I remember IOC President Thomas Bachsaid Tokyo was the best-ever prepared city to host an Olympics.\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3590, \"end\": 3603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3604, \"end\": 3610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.9361134772660147, \"rank\": 0.06302336183000465, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\"}, {\"begin\": 3620, \"end\": 3625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.187746768322841e-14, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best-ever prepared city\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that we are two months out from Paris, how is the organization looking?\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3715, \"end\": 3720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organization\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dubi:Of course, the last one in Tokyo was in a COVID context, and then you had Rio (in 2016), which were really complicated.\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3788, \"end\": 3793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.187746768322841e-14, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dubi\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3760}, {\"ngram\": \"a COVID context\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3816}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would say we are in a comparable situation to London (in 2012) with the same volume of issues to be dealt with.\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3929, \"end\": 3935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999999948164715, \"rank\": 4.5969529834513456e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a comparable situation\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3925}, {\"ngram\": \"the same volume\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing of significance at this point in time.\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"significance\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4018}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4032}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the venues are on time, but a lot of details still in the plan.\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the venues\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4056}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4068}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4079}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 4083, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, every day you would have your daily issues, but nothing of significance.\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your daily issues\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4163}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4176}, {\"ngram\": \"significance\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not feel, where I am sitting, stress in the organizing team, but rather the pressure of expectations.\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organizing team\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4262}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 4275, \"to\": 4287}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is a good context to have that level of expectation because of everything that has happened in the last two years.\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4305, \"end\": 4310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good context\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4347}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 4351, \"to\": 4362}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4384}, {\"ngram\": \"the last two years\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of the plan of Paris, which is incredibly exciting.\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4449, \"end\": 4454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the Opening Ceremony (on the Seine River),the Champions Park(celebration area at the foot of the Eiffel Tower), the fact that all the urban sports are in Paris center.\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.581427353536052e-11, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 4645, \"end\": 4650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994265636, \"rank\": 5.73228492745073e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Seine River),the Champions Park(celebration area\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4568}, {\"ngram\": \"the foot\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"all the urban sports\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The expectations are amazingly high, but also because of the political tensions, and this is where, by the way, the whole int